{"title":"暴殄天物","authors":["池北偶"],"dates":[{"year":1991,"month":12,"day":7}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"暴殄天物"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"池北偶诗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"江帆画"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你说盘中餐，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"粒粒皆辛苦；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他说碗中饭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每碗一毛五，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只顶半根烟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浪费不在乎。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"米粥倒泔水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"馒头喂牲畜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小狗吃包子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"猫咪喝牛乳。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"此等阔习气，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"并不在少数。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"粮食乱糟蹋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只因衣食足。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"劝君莫忘记，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有人仍饿肚。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（附图片）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}